<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Chieh in, na hun chengin semin,
 * Kipahnan Pa deih guol semin;
 Ziechuh Lalpa Lampi ahi,
 Nangin ziechuh hawh lo ding maw? (2)

[V2]
 2. Chieh in, semin a hun nai puoi,
 * Manna chuh van lepna ahi;
 Mihing in a hun demziek un,
 Pathien hun dem ding gingcha ki'n. (2)

[V3]
 3. Chieh in, semin, sep phat ahi,
 * Na lunggil sung hih kipak din;
 A hepihnan a hun pakchai,
 Na sepgimna chuh thawn puona. (2)

[V4]
 4. Chieh in, a phat laiin sem in,
 * Khawvel buoina a hung lien ie;
 Thatdahna paih in sem mengin,
 Thagau hukdamna hung hina. (2)

[V5]
 5. Na kawma thimah mi a thiu,
 * Thih lungmuonna la nei loin;
 Meisel la'n la de vak zingin,
 Thimna pen le vaksak ina. (2)

[V6]
 6. Sem zelin, chau loin vengin,
 * Chingthei in mangthai pui dingin;
 Khawvel muntin ah chieh unla,
 Vakmangte chuh pui lut hamun (2)

[V7]
 7. Kipak takin na chuh semin,
 * Sepgim chuh chawlhna nuom ahi;
 Moneipa Aw he pai tan la,
 Ngaiin &quot;Hung ding ka hi&quot; A tii. (2)</lyrics>
<title>GO LABOUR ON!</title>
<hymn_number>285</hymn_number>
</song>